text.plotcubic.help.admin.view_reports: Allows viewing plot reports without moderating.
text.plotcubic.help.chat_style: Change the style of messages in plot chat.
text.plotcubic.help.clear: Clean the plot and leave it as new.
text.plotcubic.help.delete: Delete the plot and you are no longer the owner.
text.plotcubic.help.deny: Ban a player from entering your plot.
text.plotcubic.help.game_mode: Change the game mode of the players on the plot.
text.plotcubic.help.help: Used to get information about commands, if you don't specify the subcommand it opens GUI with all subcommands
text.plotcubic.help.home: Teleport to a plot that belongs to you.
text.plotcubic.help.info: Used to get information about the plot you are on.
text.plotcubic.help.remove: Remove deny or trust of a user from your plot.
text.plotcubic.help.report: Report a plot that breaks the rules for a staff to moderate it.
text.plotcubic.help.teleport: Teleports you to the Plot World dimension.
text.plotcubic.help.trust: Give some permissions on the plot to a player.
text.plotcubic.help.visit: Used to visit the specified plot.
